    JsonArrayProperty  
    JsonArrayReader
    JsonArrayReader lets the caller parse the items in an array one by one, iterating through them & processing them as they're parsed.
    JsonArrayWriter
    JsonArrayWriter lets the caller serialize the items in an array one by one, iterating through them & serializing each in turn.
